00:25:14.310 --> 00:25:18.810
if we say, it gives a lot of ways
to add structure to your webpage.

00:25:18.910 --> 00:25:23.200
Be it heading, lists, tables, landmarks.

00:25:23.660 --> 00:25:29.220
It helps you to ensure that
your content of your website

00:25:29.440 --> 00:25:31.350
is in a proper structured manner.

00:25:31.530 --> 00:25:33.660
Be it ensuring that

00:25:33.820 --> 00:25:37.280
every page having a heading 1 or ensuring

00:25:37.420 --> 00:25:40.750
that the content is not structured
as a heading.

00:25:41.250 --> 00:25:45.850
You will get a kind of a panel
once you are into your website

00:25:45.950 --> 00:25:49.060
and you try to edit
the content of your website.

00:25:49.390 --> 00:25:52.220
There would be a toolbar through
which you can add

00:25:52.330 --> 00:25:55.730
such formatting to like,
you know, if you want

00:25:55.830 --> 00:25:59.370
a particular text to be heading
1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6.

00:25:59.750 --> 00:26:01.620
You can do that easily.

00:26:01.730 --> 00:26:07.610
Ensure that it is as per the hierarchy
and as per the context of your page

00:26:08.010 --> 00:26:11.610
and ensure that it is following
the hierarchical manner as well.

00:26:12.180 --> 00:26:14.180
It should start from H1 to H6.

00:26:14.210 --> 00:26:16.820
Don't forget to skip
any heading in between.

00:26:16.920 --> 00:26:19.890
That really confuses a screen reader user,

00:26:20.290 --> 00:26:24.520
because it might appear to them
that they have forgot

00:26:25.090 --> 00:26:29.260
one of the section on the page
and they might just be like--

00:26:29.360 --> 00:26:32.000
and it would be a frustrating
experience for them.

00:26:33.330 --> 00:26:36.570
When it comes to list,
there is also a way to add a list structure

00:26:36.710 --> 00:26:38.470
be it an unordered list, ordered list.

00:26:38.570 --> 00:26:43.280
You can do that using the toolbar
that is given in WordPress.

00:26:43.380 --> 00:26:47.510
You can add your information
in a sequential manner.

