we always have a comparison table
in product

00:27:25.990 --> 00:27:29.090
review section
or maybe product description section.

00:27:29.620 --> 00:27:31.460
Ensure those are well-formed.

00:27:31.560 --> 00:27:34.590
They are having appropriate
headers, column headers, row headers.

00:27:35.930 --> 00:27:37.000
You can add that.

