00:38:28.880 --> 00:38:33.550
it needs to be reachable
when using a tab key or any input device.

00:38:34.390 --> 00:38:35.990
It needs to be operable.

00:38:36.090 --> 00:38:39.260
Basically when you press any space bar

00:38:39.360 --> 00:38:42.830
or an enter key
on any particular interactive element,

00:38:43.100 --> 00:38:47.030
it needs to function something,
it needs to action out the event.

00:38:48.600 --> 00:38:51.870
Also using a mouse device,
it needs to action out the same event

00:38:52.170 --> 00:38:54.770
or any switch devices as well.

00:38:55.740 --> 00:38:58.340
It needs to have a visual focus indicator.

